					"host": [
						"{{baseUrl}}"
					],
					"path": [
						"leads"
					]
				},
				"description": "Create a new lead.\n\n**Required fields:**\n- `clientId`: Client identifier\n- `name`: Lead name\n- `phone`: Lead phone\n\n**Optional fields:**\n- `email`: Email address\n- `location`: Location\n- `source`: Lead source (default: web-form)\n- `metadata`: Additional data object"
